        operate a US subsidiary the way Meiko does (MEIKO USA, La Vergne TN) or the way Miele operates Miele
        Professional's US division. For LA operators running a Winterhalter commercial dishwasher, service options
        are limited. Most general-appliance repair companies simply decline Winterhalter calls because they don't
        have parts infrastructure. Distributors like McGrath Refrigeration and European suppliers (gastroparts.com,
        ascateringsupplies.com) handle parts supply with 5-to-14-day lead times. We're one of the few LA service
        providers with genuine Winterhalter experience and an established European parts supply relationship.
      </p>
      <p>
