        cluster specifies Winterhalter on install. German engineering, Energy+ heat recovery for operators watching
        utility costs, RoMatik XS reverse osmosis for spot-free glassware, PAY PER WASH for chain operators
        standardizing cost structures — these features matter enough at the premium end of the market that the
        no-US-service-support reality is acceptable. But only if there's someone in LA who can actually service
        the unit.
      </p>
    </div>
